<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="literally-adv">literally <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lɪtərəli/    美 /'lɪtərəli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>照字义；根据字面意思；真正地；确实地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Until next payday, I was literally without any money.
在下一次发工资之前，我真的是身无分文。</p></div></div>